#: ../source/administration/production-notes.txt:559
msgid ""
"If your host runs kernel versions ``3.5`` or later, or :abbr:`RHEL (Red "
"Hat Enterprise Linux)` / CentOS kernel ``2.6.32-303`` or later, setting "
